

     
      "Thank you for closing the threads of destiny so neatly.  I will arrange things with the authorities."  You get up to go and as you approach the door he stops you again.  "Oh, Cody.  I will tell you this as well.  I know you seek answers for the place from which you came.  A greater understanding of the why.  The secret is the Saint.  I do not know details, I only know things I have been told.  The secret is Saint Ivan.  The mystery is now to fill in what lies between the question and the answer."
     
    
